ActOld Age Security Act
SubjectAgreement and Implementing Agreement on Social Security ** French **
PrecisOrder declaring the coming into force of the AGREEMENT between the Government of Canada and the Government of the FRENCH REPUBLIC ON SOCIAL SECURITY and the IMPLEMENTING AGREEMENT CONCERNING THE AGREEMENT between the Government of Canada and the Government of the FRENCH REPUBLIC on Social Security to be the first day of the fourth month following the month in which the Contracting State shall notify the other, through diplomatic channels, of the completion of its constitutional or legislative procedures necessary for the entry into force of the Agreements.
